name: Aquila
description: The world needs more people like you. You are a rare pearl, sweet, innocent, but indestructible. You fly on your own in search of a healthier life. Everything seems destroyed and saddened, but you do not accept defeat easily and will fight for love. With the bright reflections on the attire, Aquila remains the favorable choice, bringing out positivity in whoever sets their eyes on it. You will be unique in the way you walk. Aquila embellishes your personality.
